<h1 itemprop="name" class="product_title wd-entities-title">Q-3 Syrup</h1><p class="price"><span class="woocs_price_code" data-product-id="28104"><span class="woocommerce-Price-amount amount"><span class="woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol">&#8377;</span>&nbsp;55.00</span></span></p>
<div class="woocommerce-product-details__short-description">
	<p>Q3 is an effective antipyretic, analgesic medicine for all types of fevers and their associated symptoms. Q3 bring down fever rapidly, alleviates accompanying body-ache, cold and coryza.</p>
<p>Q3 is ideal for: Inflammatory fever,Bilious fever,Eruptive fever,Septic fever,Rheumatic fever, Intermittent fever, catarrhal fever.</p>
</div>

				<a href="#tab-description" class="wd-accordion-title woodmart-accordion-title tab-title-description active">Description</a>
				<div class="woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--description panel entry-content wc-tab" id="tab-description">
					<div class="wc-tab-inner 
										">
						<div class="">
							

<p>Q3 Syrup  The action of its individual constituents is as follows.</p>
<p>1. <strong>Arsenicum Album 3C</strong> : Fever with marked exhaustion, restlessness, associated symptoms such as sneezing, burning in eyes, acid nasal discharge, thirst for small quantities of water at short intervals. Fever as a result of food poisoning.<br />
2. <strong>Belladonna 3X</strong>: Fever associated with extreme head, redness, throbbing and burning. Fever which are violent and sudden in onset.. No thirst with fever. It is excellent medicine for eruptive fevers.<br />
3. <strong>Bryonia Alb 3X</strong>: External coldness with internal heat. Headache, body aches are worse motion. Thirst for large quantities of cold water at long intervals calls for Bryonia. Fevers with hepatic complications.<br />
4. <strong>Ferrum Phosphoricum 3x</strong>: Indicated in early stages of both inflammatory and catarrhal fevers.</p>
<p>Side Effects : No side effects of Q3 are known.<br />
Contraindication: No Contraindications know.<br />
Interactions : No antidotal and inimical medicines are used in Q3. It does not interact with the action of any other medicine.</p>
<p>Presentation: Available in 60ml.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
